{"data": [{"id": "4743587", "title": "Allspring Small Company Value Fund Q3 2024 Commentary", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1287899462/image_1287899462.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Franchise business growth with earning money, copy space.\" data-id=\"1287899462\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"845px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1287899462/image_1287899462.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1287899462/image_1287899462.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1287899462/image_1287899462.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1287899462/image_1287899462.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1287899462/image_1287899462.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1287899462/image_1287899462.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1287899462/image_1287899462.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1287899462/image_1287899462.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"></p> <p class=\"item-credits\">oatawa</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Quarterly review</h2> <p>The Allspring Small Company Value Fund underperformed the benchmark for the quarter. The materials, consumer staples, and health care sectors were the primary contributors to performance, while the energy, communication services, and financials sectors detracted from performance.</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1287899462/image_1287899462.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743587-allspring-small-company-value-fund-q3-2024-commentary", "pub_date": "2024-12-11 17:40:00"}, {"id": "4743569", "title": "Slash Your 2024 Tax Bill With These Tax-Loss Stocks", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1200508619/image_1200508619.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Stock Market Crash and Escape - Global Business Strategy Exchange\" data-id=\"1200508619\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"8000px\" height=\"5000px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1200508619/image_1200508619.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1200508619/image_1200508619.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1200508619/image_1200508619.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1200508619/image_1200508619.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1200508619/image_1200508619.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1200508619/image_1200508619.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1200508619/image_1200508619.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1200508619/image_1200508619.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">sefa ozel</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>With only two trading weeks left, investors should consider booking losses <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743013-tax-loss-stocks-to-sell-before-everyone-else-does\">now before the crowd does</a>. The risk of getting ahead of the market is that those tax-loss candidates may rise within the 30-day wash rule.</p> <p>One</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1200508619/image_1200508619.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743569-slash-your-2024-tax-bill-with-these-tax-loss-stocks", "pub_date": "2024-12-11 17:35:32"}, {"id": "4743566", "title": "JPRE: Current Allocation Suggests Defensive 2025 Positioning", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1389125589/image_1389125589.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"JP Morgan in Hong Kong\" data-id=\"1389125589\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1389125589/image_1389125589.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1389125589/image_1389125589.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1389125589/image_1389125589.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1389125589/image_1389125589.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1389125589/image_1389125589.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1389125589/image_1389125589.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1389125589/image_1389125589.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1389125589/image_1389125589.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">winhorse</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Introduction</h2> <p>The JPMorgan Realty Income ETF (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSEARCA:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/JPRE\" title=\"JPMorgan Realty Income ETF\">JPRE</a></span>) has marginally outperformed the Vanguard Real Estate Index Fund ETF (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/VNQ\" title=\"Vanguard Real Estate ETF\">VNQ</a>) so far in 2024, delivering a ~12% total return against the ~10% gain for the broad U.S. real estate ETF:</p> <p></p> <p>After</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1389125589/image_1389125589.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743566-jpre-current-allocation-suggests-defensive-2025-positioning", "pub_date": "2024-12-11 17:26:12"}, {"id": "4743565", "title": "Avidity Biosciences Advances With FDA Clearance And Promising Data For Rare Diseases", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1826415391/image_1826415391.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Mecanismo de los conjugados anticuerpo-oligonucle\u00f3tido o AOC\" data-id=\"1826415391\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1826415391/image_1826415391.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1826415391/image_1826415391.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1826415391/image_1826415391.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1826415391/image_1826415391.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1826415391/image_1826415391.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1826415391/image_1826415391.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1826415391/image_1826415391.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1826415391/image_1826415391.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Love Employee/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Avidity Biosciences, Inc. (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/RNA\" title=\"Avidity Biosciences, Inc.\">RNA</a></span>) is rapidly growing into a potential leader in RNA-based genetic therapies, leveraging its Antibody Oligonucleotide Conjugates [AOCs] technology. Since my previous May 2024 article, the stock has appreciated by about 20.3%. This move likely reflects</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1826415391/image_1826415391.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743565-avidity-biosciences-advances-with-fda-clearance-and-promising-data-for-rare-diseases", "pub_date": "2024-12-11 17:25:13"}, {"id": "4743358", "title": "Invest In $95,000 BDC Portfolio For $10,000 Annual Income And Durable Compounding", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1299490409/image_1299490409.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Dollar money bag and protection shield. Ease doing business. Guaranteed deposits insurance compensation. Investment protection. Strength of the financial system. Sustainable banks.\" data-id=\"1299490409\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"702px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1299490409/image_1299490409.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1299490409/image_1299490409.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1299490409/image_1299490409.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1299490409/image_1299490409.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1299490409/image_1299490409.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1299490409/image_1299490409.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1299490409/image_1299490409.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1299490409/image_1299490409.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Andrii Yalanskyi/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Private credit and BDCs have been increasingly strengthening their roles into the overall investment game, allowing investors to calibrate the portfolio strategies with a quite unique set of risk and return factors.</p> <p>The asset class has reached more than <a href=\"https://www.mckinsey.com/industries/private-capital/our-insights/the-next-era-of-private-credit\" rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://www.mckinsey.com/industries/private-capital/our-insights/the-next-era-of-private-credit\" target=\"_blank\">$2</a></p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1299490409/image_1299490409.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743358-invest-in-95000-bdc-portfolio-for-10000-annual-income-and-durable-compounding", "pub_date": "2024-12-11 17:15:00"}, {"id": "4743561", "title": "Bank of America: Buy Now For Increased Dividends", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1001776014/image_1001776014.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Bank of America Plaza\" data-id=\"1001776014\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"3474px\" height=\"2316px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1001776014/image_1001776014.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1001776014/image_1001776014.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1001776014/image_1001776014.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1001776014/image_1001776014.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1001776014/image_1001776014.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1001776014/image_1001776014.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1001776014/image_1001776014.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1001776014/image_1001776014.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">tupungato</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The financial sector (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/XLF\" title=\"Financial Select Sector SPDR\u00ae Fund ETF\">XLF</a>) has performed well in 2024, and even better in Q4 following the US election. Bank of America (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/BAC\" title=\"Bank of America Corporation\">BAC</a></span>) has kept pace and looks set to challenge its all-time high of $55 next year. This</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1001776014/image_1001776014.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743561-bank-of-america-buy-now-for-increased-dividends", "pub_date": "2024-12-11 17:04:15"}, {"id": "4743506", "title": "SP500 Likely To Underperform In 2025, But Still One Of The Best Long-Term Investments", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1420095549/image_1420095549.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"S&amp;P 500 stock market index crash and bear market due to financial crisis and recession in US. Wooden blocks in with coins in dark black background.\" data-id=\"1420095549\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1420095549/image_1420095549.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1420095549/image_1420095549.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1420095549/image_1420095549.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1420095549/image_1420095549.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1420095549/image_1420095549.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1420095549/image_1420095549.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1420095549/image_1420095549.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1420095549/image_1420095549.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">John Kevin</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>The S&amp;P 500 Investment Thesis</h2> <p>Seeking Alpha has started the <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4740710-new-article-competition-2025-market-prediction\">Market Prediction 2025 contest</a> on their article contest account, and I thought it would be a good time to think about the S&amp;P 500 (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSEARCA:</span></p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1420095549/image_1420095549.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743506-sp500-may-underperform-2025-but-still-good-long-term-investment", "pub_date": "2024-12-11 17:00:00"}, {"id": "4743557", "title": "Waymo Skips Uber, But I Am Not Worried", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1311247904/image_1311247904.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Uber car waiting for customer\" data-id=\"1311247904\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"6240px\" height=\"4160px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1311247904/image_1311247904.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1311247904/image_1311247904.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1311247904/image_1311247904.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1311247904/image_1311247904.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1311247904/image_1311247904.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1311247904/image_1311247904.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1311247904/im